                <p>
                  Migrate your data, questions, and groups smoothly to <a
                    href="/cloud/">Metabase Cloud</a
                  >. Keep it close to you with hosting options in the US,
                  Europe, Latin America, or Asia-Pacific.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="card">
                <svg
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  width="24"
                  height="24"
                  fill="none"
                  ><path
                    stroke="#509EE3"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="1.5"
