                    dashboards, or use the <a
                      href="/product/embedded-analytics-sdk">React SDK</a
                    > for advanced setups as your needs grow
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <b>Manage with zero code.</b> Empower your data team (or any
                    non-dev teammates) to manage permissions, iterate on dashboards
                    and visualizations, and refine reports—without bugging devs
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <b>Customizable to fit your product.</b> White-labeling, dynamic
                    styling, and interactive controls from view-only to full data
                    discovery
                  </li>
                </ul>
                <a href="/product/embedded-analytics"
                  >Learn more <img
                    alt="Chevron Blue Right"
                    class="chevron-blue-right"
                    src="/images/chevron_blue_right.svg"
                  /></a
